window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>I never had a say in my future—until now.</p> <p>When the truth about the blood oath is revealed, Calla has a devastating choice to make: leave the vampires she’s caught feelings for or stay and fight for the life she’s built with them. And each choice has severe, irreversible consequences.</p> <p>With the hunters carrying out attacks of their own and a betrayal by someone close to Calla, she remains stuck in a whirlwind of fear and confusion. Not to mention the darkness still lurking in Kade and the psychotic vampire Selene lurking in the shadows.</p> <p>Faced with a life-altering ultimatum, Calla must choose to give up everything she has come to know, or the future she is terrified to want.</p> <p><i>Fated in Ruby</i> is the fourth installment in the bloody sexy Blood Oath series!</p>"; 
